00053 std::string
00054 SgAsmBlock::reason_str(bool do_pad, unsigned r)
00055 {
00056     using namespace StringUtility; // for add_to_reason_string()
00057     std::string result;
00058 
00059     if (r & BLK_LEFTOVERS) {
00060         add_to_reason_string(result, true, do_pad, "L", "leftovers");
00061     } else if (r & BLK_PADDING) {
00062         add_to_reason_string(result, true, do_pad, "N", "padding");
00063     } else if (r & BLK_FRAGMENT) {
00064         add_to_reason_string(result, true, do_pad, "F", "fragment");
00065     } else if (r & BLK_JUMPTABLE) {
00066         add_to_reason_string(result, true, do_pad, "J", "jumptable");
00067     } else {
00068         add_to_reason_string(result, (r & BLK_ENTRY_POINT),  do_pad, "E", "entry point");
00069     }
00070 
00071     if (r & BLK_CFGHEAD) {
00072         add_to_reason_string(result, true, do_pad, "H", "CFG head");
00073     } else if (r & BLK_GRAPH1) {
00074         add_to_reason_string(result, true, do_pad, "1", "graph-1");
00075     } else if (r & BLK_GRAPH2) {
00076         add_to_reason_string(result, true, do_pad, "2", "graph-2");
00077     } else {
00078         add_to_reason_string(result, (r & BLK_GRAPH3), do_pad, "3", "graph-3");
00079     }
00080 
00081     if (r & BLK_USERDEF) {
00082         add_to_reason_string(result, true, do_pad, "U", "user defined");
00083     } else {
00084         char abbr[32], full[64];
00085         int width = snprintf(abbr, sizeof abbr, "%u", BLK_MISCMASK);
00086         snprintf(abbr, sizeof abbr, "M%0*u", width, (r & BLK_MISCMASK));
00087         abbr[sizeof(abbr)-1] = '\0';
00088         if (!do_pad) {
00089             std::string miscname = stringifySgAsmBlockReason((r & BLK_MISCMASK), "BLK_");
00090             if (miscname.empty() || miscname[0]=='(') {
00091                 snprintf(full, sizeof full, "misc-%u", (r & BLK_MISCMASK));
00092             } else {
00093                 for (size_t i=0; i<miscname.size(); ++i)
00094                     miscname[i] = tolower(miscname[i]);
00095                 strncpy(full, miscname.c_str(), sizeof full);
00096             }
00097             full[sizeof(full)-1] = '\0';
00098         } else {
00099             full[0] = '\0';
00100         }
00101         add_to_reason_string(result, (r & BLK_MISCMASK), do_pad, abbr, full);
00102     }
00103     return result;
00104 }
